{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/87970", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/87970/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/87970/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/87970/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/87970", "id": 968868139, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU5Njg4NjgxMzk=", "number": 87970, "title": "`INT::div_euclid` and `INT::rem_euclid` return incorrect values for negative numerators", "user": {"login": "toothbrush7777777", "id": 8356617, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjgzNTY2MTc=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8356617?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777", "html_url": "https://github.com/toothbrush7777777", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 234956, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyMzQ5NTY=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/A-codegen", "name": "A-codegen", "color": "f7e101", "default": false, "description": "Area: Code generation"}, {"id": 211668100, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyMTE2NjgxMDA=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/T-compiler", "name": "T-compiler", "color": "bfd4f2", "default": false, "description": "Relevant to the compiler team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue."}, {"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 0, "created_at": "2021-08-12T13:50:02Z", "updated_at": "2021-08-12T14:12:23Z", "closed_at": "2021-08-12T14:12:23Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "The results of `SIGNED_INT::div_euclid` and `SIGNED_INT::rem_euclid` are always incorrect when `a % b != 0 && a.is_negative()` (where `a` is the dividend and `b` is the divisor).\r\n\r\n**I tried something similar to this code:**\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nfn main() {\r\n    assert_eq!(div(-32768, -32767), (1, 1));\r\n}\r\nfn div(num: i16, div: i16) -> (i16, i16) {\r\n    (num.div_euclid(div), num.rem_euclid(div))\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n**I expected to see this happen:**\r\nThe assert should not fire.\r\n\r\n**Instead, this happened:**\r\nThe assert fired. The return value is `(2, 32766)` instead of `(1, 1)`.\r\n\r\n[More general test case on playground](https://play.rust-lang.org/?version=stable&mode=release&edition=2018&gist=1df5a3258411582c177f2a818b271903)\r\n\r\n### Meta\r\n\r\nThis bug exists in the latest stable, beta and nightly.\r\nThe bug appears to have been present since 1.38, when `div_euclid` and `rem_euclid` where introduced.\r\nThe profile (release or debug) makes no difference.", "closed_by": {"login": "toothbrush7777777", "id": 8356617, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjgzNTY2MTc=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8356617?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777", "html_url": "https://github.com/toothbrush7777777", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/toothbrush7777777/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/87970/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/87970/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}